                    attendee.participationType === '2-day' ? 'bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600' : 'bg-amber-50 text-amber-600'
                  }`}>
                    {attendee.participationType === '2-day' ? '两天全程 VIP' : '单日体验嘉宾'}
                  </span>
